{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"A few words about how I got started,"},{"time":2000,"text":"and it has a lot to do with happiness, actually."},{"time":6000,"text":"When I was a very young child, I was extremely introverted"},{"time":9000,"text":"and very much to myself."},{"time":12000,"text":"And, kind of as a way of surviving,"},{"time":15000,"text":"I would go into my own very personal space,"},{"time":18000,"text":"and I would make things."},{"time":20000,"text":"I would make things for people"},{"time":22000,"text":"as a way of, you know, giving, showing them my love."},{"time":26000,"text":"I would go into these private places,"},{"time":29000,"text":"and I would put my ideas and my passions into objects --"},{"time":33000,"text":"and sort of learning how to speak with my hands."},{"time":36000,"text":"So, the whole activity of working with my hands and creating objects"},{"time":40000,"text":"is very much connected with not only the idea realm,"},{"time":45000,"text":"but also with very much the feeling realm."},{"time":49000,"text":"And the ideas are very disparate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53000,"text":"I'm going to show you many different kinds of pieces,"},{"time":56000,"text":"and there's no real connection between one or the other,"},{"time":59000,"text":"except that they sort of come out of my brain,"},{"time":61000,"text":"and they're all different sort of thoughts that are triggered"},{"time":65000,"text":"by looking at life, and seeing nature and seeing objects,"},{"time":69000,"text":"and just having kind of playful random thoughts about things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73000,"text":"When I was a child, I started to explore motion."},{"time":81000,"text":"I fell in love with the way things moved,"},{"time":83000,"text":"so I started to explore motion by making little flipbooks."},{"time":88000,"text":"And this is one that I did, probably like when I was around seventh grade,"},{"time":92000,"text":"and I remember when I was doing this,"},{"time":95000,"text":"I was thinking about that little rock there,"},{"time":98000,"text":"and the pathway of the vehicles as they would fly through the air,"},{"time":103000,"text":"and how the characters --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":105000,"text":"(Laughter) --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":106000,"text":"would come shooting out of the car,"},{"time":108000,"text":"so, on my mind, I was thinking about the trajectory of the vehicles."},{"time":115000,"text":"And of course, when you're a little kid, there's always destruction."},{"time":118000,"text":"So, it has to end with this --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":120000,"text":"(Laughter) --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":121000,"text":"gratuitous violence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":123000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":125000,"text":"So that was how I first started to explore the way things moved,"},{"time":131000,"text":"and expressed it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133000,"text":"Now, when I went to college,"},{"time":135000,"text":"I found myself making fairly complicated, fragile machines."},{"time":142000,"text":"And this really came about"},{"time":145000,"text":"from having many different kinds of interests."},{"time":148000,"text":"When I was in high school, I loved to program computers,"},{"time":151000,"text":"so I sort of liked the logical flow of events."},{"time":156000,"text":"I was also very interested in perhaps going into surgery"},{"time":161000,"text":"and becoming a surgeon,"},{"time":163000,"text":"because it meant working with my hands"},{"time":165000,"text":"in a very focused, intense way."},{"time":168000,"text":"So, I started taking art courses,"},{"time":170000,"text":"and I found a way to make sculpture"},{"time":173000,"text":"that brought together my love for being very precise with my hands,"},{"time":177000,"text":"with coming up with different kinds of logical flows of energy through a system."},{"time":187000,"text":"And also, working with wire -- everything that I did"},{"time":193000,"text":"was both a visual and a mechanical engineering decision"},{"time":199000,"text":"at the same time."},{"time":201000,"text":"So, I was able to sort of exercise all of that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203000,"text":"Now, this kind of machine is as close as I can get to painting."},{"time":209000,"text":"And it's full of many little trivial end points,"},{"time":214000,"text":"like there's a little foot here that just drags around in circles"},{"time":219000,"text":"and it doesn't really mean anything."},{"time":221000,"text":"It's really just for the sort of joy of its own triviality."},{"time":227000,"text":"The connection I have with engineering"},{"time":230000,"text":"is the same as any other engineer, in that I love to solve problems."},{"time":235000,"text":"I love to figure things out,"},{"time":237000,"text":"but the end result of what I'm doing is really completely ambiguous."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":245000,"text":"That's pretty ambiguous."}]},{"cues":[{"time":247000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":249000,"text":"The next piece that is going to come up"},{"time":254000,"text":"is an example of a kind of machine that is fairly complex."},{"time":264000,"text":"I gave myself the problem."},{"time":266000,"text":"Since I'm always liking to solve problems,"},{"time":268000,"text":"I gave myself the problem of turning a crank in one direction,"},{"time":272000,"text":"and solving all of the mechanical problems"},{"time":275000,"text":"for getting this little man to walk back and forth."},{"time":279000,"text":"So, when I started this, I didn't have an overall plan for the machine,"},{"time":284000,"text":"but I did have a sense of the gesture,"},{"time":287000,"text":"and a sense of the shape and how it would occupy space."},{"time":291000,"text":"And then it was a matter of starting from one point"},{"time":294000,"text":"and sort of building to that final point."},{"time":298000,"text":"That little gear there switches back and forth to change direction."},{"time":303000,"text":"And that's a little found object."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307000,"text":"So a lot of the pieces that I've made,"},{"time":310000,"text":"they involve found objects."},{"time":314000,"text":"And it really -- it's almost like doing visual puns all the time."},{"time":322000,"text":"When I see objects, I imagine them in motion."},{"time":325000,"text":"I imagine what can be said with them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327000,"text":"This next one here, \"Machine with Wishbone,\""},{"time":331000,"text":"it came about from playing with this wishbone after dinner."},{"time":338000,"text":"You know, they say, never play with your food --"},{"time":340000,"text":"but I always play with things."},{"time":342000,"text":"So, I had this wishbone, and I thought,"},{"time":344000,"text":"it's kind of like a cowboy who's been on his horse for too long."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":348000,"text":"And I started to make him walk across the table,"},{"time":351000,"text":"and I thought, \"Oh, I can make a little machine that will do that.\""},{"time":356000,"text":"So, I made this device, linked it up, and the wishbone walks."},{"time":362000,"text":"And because the wishbone is bone -- it's animal --"},{"time":365000,"text":"it's sort of a point where I think we can enter into it."},{"time":371000,"text":"And that's the whole piece."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":374000,"text":"That's about that big."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":382000,"text":"This kind of work is also very much like puppetry,"},{"time":387000,"text":"where the found object is, in a sense, the puppet,"},{"time":391000,"text":"and I'm the puppeteer at first, because I'm playing with an object."},{"time":396000,"text":"But then I make the machine, which is sort of the stand-in for me,"},{"time":400000,"text":"and it is able to achieve the action that I want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":405000,"text":"The next piece I'll show you is a much more conceptual thought,"},{"time":412000,"text":"and it's a little piece called \"Cory's Yellow Chair.\""},{"time":416000,"text":"I had this image in my mind, when I saw my son's little chair,"},{"time":421000,"text":"and I saw it explode up and out."},{"time":426000,"text":"And --"},{"time":430000,"text":"so the way I saw this in my mind at first,"},{"time":433000,"text":"was that the pieces would explode up and out with infinite speed,"},{"time":437000,"text":"and the pieces would move far out,"},{"time":439000,"text":"and then they would begin to be pulled back"},{"time":441000,"text":"with a kind of a gravitational feel,"},{"time":443000,"text":"to the point where they would approach infinite speed back to the center."},{"time":447000,"text":"And they would coalesce for just a moment,"},{"time":450000,"text":"so you could perceive that there was a chair there."},{"time":453000,"text":"For me, it's kind of a feeling about the fleetingness of the present moment,"},{"time":459000,"text":"and I wanted to express that."},{"time":461000,"text":"Now, the machine is -- in this case, it's a real approximation of that,"},{"time":466000,"text":"because obviously you can't move physical matter"},{"time":469000,"text":"infinitely with infinite speed and have it stop instantaneously."},{"time":473000,"text":"This whole thing is about four feet wide,"},{"time":477000,"text":"and the chair itself is only about a few inches."}]},{"cues":[{"time":480000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":485000,"text":"Now, this is a funny sort of conceptual thing,"},{"time":488000,"text":"and yesterday we were talking about Danny Hillis' \"10,000 Year Clock.\""},{"time":493000,"text":"So, we have a motor here on the left,"},{"time":495000,"text":"and it goes through a gear train."},{"time":498000,"text":"There are 12 pairs of 50:1 reductions,"},{"time":503000,"text":"so that means that the final speed of that gear on the end"},{"time":508000,"text":"is so slow that it would take two trillion years to turn once."},{"time":512000,"text":"So I've invented it in concrete, because it doesn't really matter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":515000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":516000,"text":"Because it could run all the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":518000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":519000,"text":"Now, a completely different thought."},{"time":523000,"text":"I'm always imagining myself in different situations."},{"time":527000,"text":"I'm imagining myself as a machine."},{"time":529000,"text":"What would I love?"},{"time":531000,"text":"I would love to be bathed in oil."}]},{"cues":[{"time":533000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":534000,"text":"So, this machine does nothing but just bathe itself in oil."}]},{"cues":[{"time":539000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":541000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":545000,"text":"And it's really, just sort of --"},{"time":548000,"text":"for me, it was just really about the lusciousness of oil."}]},{"cues":[{"time":551000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":552000,"text":"And then, I got a call from a friend"},{"time":555000,"text":"who wanted to have a show of erotic art,"},{"time":558000,"text":"and I didn't have any pieces."},{"time":560000,"text":"But when she suggested to be in the show, this piece came to mind."},{"time":564000,"text":"So, it's sort of related, but you can see it's much more overtly erotic."},{"time":570000,"text":"And this one I call \"Machine with Grease.\""},{"time":573000,"text":"It's just continually ejaculating, and it's --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":575000,"text":"(Laughter) --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":576000,"text":"this is a happy machine, I'll tell you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":579000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":580000,"text":"It's definitely happy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":584000,"text":"From an engineering point of view,"},{"time":587000,"text":"this is just a little four-bar linkage."},{"time":589000,"text":"And then again, this is a found object, a little fan that I found."},{"time":594000,"text":"And I thought, what about the gesture of opening the fan,"},{"time":597000,"text":"and how simply could I state something."},{"time":600000,"text":"And, in a case like this, I'm trying to make something which is clear"},{"time":608000,"text":"but also not suggestive of any particular kind of animal or plant."}]},{"cues":[{"time":615000,"text":"For me, the process is very important,"},{"time":620000,"text":"because I'm inventing machines,"},{"time":622000,"text":"but I'm also inventing tools to make machines,"},{"time":625000,"text":"and the whole thing is all sort of wrapped up from the beginning."},{"time":628000,"text":"So this is a little wire-bending tool."},{"time":631000,"text":"After many years of bending gears with a pair of pliers,"},{"time":634000,"text":"I made that tool, and then I made this other tool"},{"time":637000,"text":"for sort of centering gears very quickly --"},{"time":641000,"text":"sort of developing my own little world of technology."},{"time":644000,"text":"My life completely changed when I found a spot welder."}]},{"cues":[{"time":650000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":651000,"text":"And that was that tool."},{"time":653000,"text":"It completely changed what I could do."},{"time":655000,"text":"Now here, I'm going to do a very poor job of silver soldering."},{"time":660000,"text":"This is not the way they teach you to silver solder when you're in school."},{"time":665000,"text":"I just like, throw it in."},{"time":667000,"text":"I mean, real jewelers put little bits of solder in."},{"time":670000,"text":"So, that's a finished gear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":674000,"text":"When I moved to Boston,"},{"time":676000,"text":"I joined a group called the World Sculpture Racing Society."}]},{"cues":[{"time":681000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":682000,"text":"And the idea, their premise was that we wanted to show"},{"time":689000,"text":"pieces of sculpture on the street,"},{"time":691000,"text":"and there'd be no subjective decision about what was the best."},{"time":695000,"text":"It would be -- whatever came across the finish line first would be the winner."}]},{"cues":[{"time":697000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":698000,"text":"So I made -- this is my first racing sculpture,"},{"time":702000,"text":"and I thought, \"Oh, I'm going to make a cart,"},{"time":704000,"text":"and I'm going to have it --"},{"time":706000,"text":"I'm going to have my hand writing 'faster,'"},{"time":708000,"text":"so as I run down the street, the cart's going to talk to me"},{"time":712000,"text":"and it's going to go, 'Faster, faster!' \""},{"time":715000,"text":"So, that's what it does."}]},{"cues":[{"time":717000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":718000,"text":"But then in the end, what I decided"},{"time":723000,"text":"was every time you finish writing the word,"},{"time":726000,"text":"I would stop and I would give the card to somebody on the side of the road."},{"time":730000,"text":"So I would never win the race because I'm always stopping."},{"time":733000,"text":"But I had a lot of fun."}]},{"cues":[{"time":735000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":741000,"text":"Now, I only have two and a half minutes -- I'm going to play this."},{"time":745000,"text":"This is a piece that, for me, is in some ways"},{"time":751000,"text":"the most complete kind of piece."},{"time":753000,"text":"Because when I was a kid, I also played a lot of guitar."},{"time":755000,"text":"And when I had this thought,"},{"time":759000,"text":"I was imagining that I would make --"},{"time":761000,"text":"I would have a whole machine theater evening,"},{"time":764000,"text":"where I would -- you would have an audience,"},{"time":766000,"text":"the curtain would open, and you'd be entertained by machines on stage."},{"time":770000,"text":"So, I imagined a very simple gestural dance"},{"time":773000,"text":"that would be between a machine and just a very simple chair, and ...\n"},{"time":789000,"text":"When I'm making these pieces, I'm always trying to find a point"},{"time":793000,"text":"where I'm saying something very clearly and it's very simple,"},{"time":804000,"text":"but also at the same time it's very ambiguous."},{"time":807000,"text":"And I think there's a point between simplicity and ambiguity"},{"time":812000,"text":"which can allow a viewer to perhaps take something from it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":821000,"text":"And that leads me to the thought that all of these pieces"},{"time":825000,"text":"start off in my own mind, in my heart,"},{"time":829000,"text":"and I do my best at finding ways to express them with materials,"},{"time":836000,"text":"and it always feels really crude."},{"time":838000,"text":"It's always a struggle,"},{"time":841000,"text":"but somehow I manage to sort of get this thought"},{"time":845000,"text":"out into an object, and then it's there, OK."},{"time":849000,"text":"It means nothing at all."},{"time":851000,"text":"The object itself just means nothing."},{"time":853000,"text":"Once it's perceived, and someone brings it into their own mind,"},{"time":858000,"text":"then there's a cycle that has been completed."},{"time":863000,"text":"And to me, that's the most important thing"},{"time":865000,"text":"because, ever since being a kid, I've wanted to communicate my passion and love."},{"time":870000,"text":"And that means the complete cycle of coming from inside,"},{"time":875000,"text":"out to the physical, to someone perceiving it."},{"time":883000,"text":"So I'll just let this chair come down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":915000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":916000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":917000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}